{"tid":1359484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貴州省水城縣山泥傾瀉至少11死　34人失蹤","createTime":"2019-07-24T06:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T07:01:00.000Z","uid":15564,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fab40aa68ec21109ad8c34c19de6db1b5f49af37","tid":1359484,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:51:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">2019-07-24 HKT 14:23</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1470154_1_20190724143506.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1470154_1_20190724143506.jpg&h=04adad1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">貴州省水城縣雞場鎮發生山泥傾瀉。（貴州消防微博圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n貴州省水城縣雞場鎮發生山泥傾瀉， 當局至今救出22人，其中11人死亡，初步認為有34人失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n當局初步核實，21間房屋被山泥掩埋，估計滑下的山泥多達200萬立方米。<br />\n<br />\n事發在昨晚9時許，而由於山泥傾瀉的面積大而且不穩定、加上落雨，增加救援困難。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470154-20190724.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470154-20190724.htm&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=51f5bf1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470154-20190724.htm&h=4a11e903\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470154-20190724.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c4fee4f57eea46c222f6d141a617f98f653f96f0","tid":1359484,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"大陸關我撚事<br />\n爆左先同我地講<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"}]}